the dow jones edged up to its ninth record closing high in a row on monday , while the s & p 500 ended slightly higher , led by gains in technology and consumer-focused companies .
the dow jones industrial average added 26 points , or 0.12 % , to close at 22,118 .
the s & p 500 climbed four points , or 0.16 % , to 2,481 and the nasdaq composite added 32 points , or 0.51 % , to end at 6,38 .
in asia , japan 's nikkei 225 slipped 0.31 % while south korea 's benchmark kospi index fell 0.3 % .
in australia , the s & p/asx 200 was down 0.82 % , while hong kong 's hang seng index declined 0.15 % .
the shanghai composite was down 0.12 % and the shenzhen composite fell 0.08 % .
